txt.en: Perform valiant deeds among the snows of the Misty Mountains.
Complete quests within the Misty Mountains.

Rising up as a great wall on the eastern border of Eriador, the Misty Mountains have long proven a formidable obstacle to travellers. Goblins are known to infest warrens dug beneath the mountains, while giants stride among the peaks capriciously threatening those who attempt to pass through its snow-swept ways.
